---
const bg = "/hero/hero3.webp";
---

<section class="v-hero v-hero--clean" aria-label="Hero">
  <!-- Background -->
  <div class="v-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <img
      src={bg}
      alt=""
      loading="eager"
      decoding="async"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <div class="v-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="v-hero-noise"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 w-full">
    <div class="v-hero-center">
      <div class="v-hero-content">
        <h1 class="v-hero-title">
          Construí <span class="v-accent">tu negocio digital</span> sobre terreno firme.
        </h1>

        <p class="v-hero-subtitle">
          Desarrollamos infraestructura de alto rendimiento diseñada para durar. Una base técnica impecable, SEO de raíz y un panel de control simple para que tu web sea el motor que impulsa tus ventas, no una carga.
        </p>

        <div class="v-hero-cta">
          <a
            href="/es/workover"
            class="v-cta v-cta--primary v-focus-ring v-anim"
          >
            Workover Web
          </a>

          <a
            href="/es/portafolio"
            class="v-cta v-cta--ghost v-focus-ring v-anim v-cta--far"
          >
            Portafolio
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="v-hero-micro" aria-label="Highlights">
          <span>SEO técnico sin humo</span>
          <span class="sep">•</span>
          <span>Performance (CWV)</span>
          <span class="sep">•</span>
          <span>Tracking útil</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style is:inline>
    /* =========================================================
       HERO CLEAN — sin island/card
       - No cambia entre modo claro/oscuro (estilo portada)
       ========================================================= */

    .v-hero--clean {
      min-height: 100svh;
      padding-top: var(--header-h);
      padding-bottom: 32px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .v-hero-center {
      min-height: calc(100svh - var(--header-h) - 32px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .v-hero-content {
      width: min(980px, 100%);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .v-hero-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      font-size: clamp(36px, 4.6vw, 64px);
      text-shadow: 0 10px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    }

    .v-hero-subtitle {
      margin: 16px auto 0;
      max-width: 62ch;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      text-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }

    /* CTAs */
    .v-hero-cta {
      margin-top: 22px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .v-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 650;
      text-decoration: none;
      user-select: none;
      min-width: 120px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .v-cta--primary {
      background: rgb(var(--accent1));
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.22);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .v-cta--ghost {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    }

    .v-cta--ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
      border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    }

    .v-cta--far {
      margin-left: 14px;
    }

    /* Micro line */
    .v-hero-micro {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      text-shadow: 0 8px 26px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    }

    .v-hero-micro .sep {
      opacity: 0.55;
    }

    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .v-cta {
        min-width: 0;
        padding: 12px 16px;
      }

      .v-cta--far {
        margin-left: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
